{"tid":2009973,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"10/05 大量25K社團份子於尖咀鐘樓收陀地","createTime":"2020-05-10T06:37:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T08:25:47.000Z","uid":186,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bb7c22ed48a8145ce4b6e28b6e351059c6be2a1b","tid":2009973,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T06:37:24.000Z","msg":"黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427063fc83b2f50f938546323d035a81908c92b6","tid":2009973,"uid":186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T06:39:04.000Z","msg":"黑社會收入來源一般涉及<span style=\"color: red;\">暴力、詐騙、色情、聚賭和毒品</span>等行為或交易，有時也會旁及傳統營生方法，但依然包括了綁標、恐嚇等，行政當局對這些商業行為大多定為非法，不過組織通常可以透過法律漏洞的形式存續下去。<br />\n<br />\n黑社會各社團之間也經常為利益而展開暴力衝突，影響社會安寧。由於黑社會生存於規範社會之外，卻以規範社會為利基，這種影子政府的存於使各地政府均致力打擊以避免失去威信。有些黑社會勢力已經超過規範社會的政府，如果前者較有效率，後者會逐漸成為擺設。同時政府又會以種種方法與黑社會合作，兩者形成一個完整的社會，而黑社會是其陰暗面。"},{"pid":"94d2fefee87f1a649becc912439d87c9160fd8ce","tid":2009973,"uid":186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T06:39:25.000Z","msg":"有5名市民被25K成員恐嚇中"},{"pid":"108935c2b08c592d6ca9cc9003f558e54029e700","tid":2009973,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T06:39:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a9a2b3cec359dbb93a7b827628cecca9af23d9","tid":2009973,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T06:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f10a638d62b82499cecbf28cac7f91613343d7d","tid":2009973,"uid":186,"like